Tentu saja tidak.
Aku hanya liburan panjang.

44
00:02:29,535 --> 00:02:30,936
Aku akan ke India.

45
00:02:32,105 --> 00:02:33,135
Benarkah?

46
00:02:33,265 --> 00:02:36,475
Kenapa kau jadi emosional?

47
00:02:36,676 --> 00:02:38,945
