164
00:11:00,975 --> 00:11:02,846
Tidak, kau harus berusaha
lebih keras lagi.

165
00:11:05,586 --> 00:11:07,255
Si Geu Rim...

166
00:11:08,086 --> 00:11:11,326
Seorang penulis tak boleh
ke hotel bersama Soo Ho.

167
00:11:11,586 --> 00:11:12,826
