00:30:36,586 --> 00:30:37,925
Kenapa kau berterima kasih padaku?

459
00:30:37,925 --> 00:30:41,296
Karena Anda tak mengganggu kami
saat siaran kami lancar.

460
00:30:41,526 --> 00:30:44,996
