00:32:32,336 --> 00:32:34,276
Lucu melihatmu cemburu.

486
00:32:34,736 --> 00:32:37,476
"Cemburu"?

487
00:32:37,476 --> 00:32:39,046
Aku tidak cemburu.

488
00:32:39,046 --> 00:32:41,175
