00:36:03,576 --> 00:36:04,945
<i>Mana mungkin kau paham?</i>

548
00:36:05,445 --> 00:36:07,016
<i>Kau tidak kekurangan apapun...,</i>

549
00:36:07,315 --> 00:36:09,155
<i>...dan bisa menikmati kenyamanan hidupmu.</i>

550
00:36:10,925 --> 00:36:12,385
Aku juga pernah merasa
tidak nyaman.

551
00:36:12,726 --> 00:36:14,195
Pernah, tapi...

552
00:36:14,195 --> 00:36:16,496
<i>Apa maksudmu?</i>

